{"tid":1550970,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蜘蛛俠加入香港5大訴求運動聯會","createTime":"2019-09-07T19:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T19:16:40.000Z","uid":74099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca1f8fbd827ace3250b7fe7b8853b76bd919eba3","tid":1550970,"uid":74099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:16:00.000Z","msg":"蜘蛛俠剛辦完退出MCU會籍，馬上趕黎香港加入運動會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n據消息人士透露，蜘蛛俠参加咗一項跳閘比賽，賽後一直以招牌姿勢停响入閘機上，紋絲不動，同香港人齊上齊落。<br />\n消息人士表示除蜘蛛俠外，蝙蝠俠亦將會駕駛蝙蝠車参加和你塞活動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis7nR3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis7nR3.jpg&h=2b4db272&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59207db141beffa0471cc2f4daa2e63c90e40ff9","tid":1550970,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:16:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76b75a439528560f95e25be72904e53ce542e983","tid":1550970,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T19:16:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}